  "description": [
    "Page Four People Of New Jersey City And New York Defeat Race Mixing Plan To Give Tax Money To Negroes Puerhi Ricans Is Killed Effort To Integrate All Fifth Grades In City Of Englewood Whipped By Voters White people everywhere arc getting fed up on this crazy scheme to force the mixing of the white and Negro races A recent attempt has been voted down in Englewood New Jersey and another has been voted down in the State of New York In Englewood New Jersey a simple proposition to establish a citywide in tegrated fifth grade as a step towards reducing what they call the racial im balance in the elementary schools was submitted to a referendum The proposition was turned down by a vote of 5825 to 1549 New York Legislature The only ward in the city voting in favor of the proposition was the fourth ward which is largely Negro In this ward the vote was 508 to 297 for the proposition Then the legislature in New York sub mitted to the people of the State the craziest proposition ever heard of and it was turned down by the people in the election of November 6th This crazy"
  ],
